    <p id="btsNewOnGS" class="smallText1"><strong>New On GreatSchools</strong></p>
    
    <h4 class="subhead6"><a href="/backToSchool/backToSchoolChecklist.page" onclick="if (s.tl) {s.tl(this,'o', 'BTS2010_Checklist_Promo');};jQuery('#btsChecklistBubble').hide()">Back-to-School Checklist</a></h4>


    <p class="text3">Take five easy steps to ensure you're ready for the new school year and you'll get 25% off school supplies from our partner, <a href="http://www.carolinapad.com/" target="new">Carolina Pad</a>. <strong>Free notebook for the first 2,500 to finish!</strong></p>


    
    <p class="text1"><strong><a id="getStarted" href="/backToSchool/backToSchoolChecklist.page" onclick="if (s.tl) {s.tl(this,'o', 'BTS2010_Checklist_Promo');};jQuery('#btsChecklistBubble').hide()">Get started <span class="alertDoubleArrow">&amp;#187;</span></a></strong></p>


    <p id="btsBubbleOpts" class="smallText1"><a class="btsSmallLink" href="#" id="btsChecklistBubbleRemindLater">Remind me later</a> |
    <a class="btsSmallLink" id="btsChecklistBubbleNoThanks" href="#">No thanks</a></p>
